            "!Alissa<br>modOH, COME ON!<br>modI WAS 10 MINUTES LATE.<br>modUUUUUGGGGGGHH!!!<pg>Alissa<br>modTHAT'S IT!<br>modI'VE HAD IT!<br>modI'M CAMPING HERE!<pg>Alissa<br>modDON'T YOU DARE!<br>modTHIS IS MY SPOT!<br>modYOU'LL REGRET IT, KID!",
