            "!Stratin the Blade <br>modThe manor’s hallways are blocked by <br>modfurniture and boxes.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Stratin the Blade <br>modDon’t be afraid to use the windows to go<br>modoutside.<br>mod<pg>Stratin the Blade <br>modI pity those who can’t just fly through <br>modeverything in a straight line.<br>mod",
            "!Stratin the Blade <br>mod<br>modSo you’re going to that dreaded island, then? <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Stratin the Blade <br>modTake my advice and do not touch that lava! <br>modEven if it looks and smells delicious! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Stratin the Blade <br>mod<br>modAnd yes, that’s how I died.<br>mod<pg>Stratin the Blade <br>modThe secret of the lava… many have tried and<br>modfailed to discover the secrets of Don<br>modSalserissimo and his volcano.",
            "!Shamo<br>modPsst! <br>modYou! <br>modYes, you!<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modIf you want to know any rumors, I’m your <br>modguy! <br>mod<pg>Shamo<br>modI heard this one from my cousin’s second<br>modwife’s neighbor! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modIn the most gossipy apartment floor, there<br>modis one vacant room with some treasure<br>modinside! <nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modThat one floor left me a little:<br>modPurplexed!  <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modTa-dah!<br>mod<br>mod<pg>Shamo<br>modSome say, that you can find a room full of<br>modgold and treasures somewhere in the<br>modMoth Queen’s big tree! <nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>mod<br>modIt’s crawling with strong foes, so beware!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modTa-dah! <br>mod<br>mod<pg>Shamo<br>modI read in some online forum that you can<br>moduse projectiles to distract certain enemies! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>mod<br>modI haven’t tried this one myself, but…<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modTa-dah!<br>mod<br>mod<pg>Shamo<br>modCome back later, curious kid! <br>modI may have some new rumors later!  <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modTa-dah!<br>mod<br>mod",
            "!Shamo<br>modPsst! <br>modYou! <br>modYes, you!<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modI have some new rumors! <br>modWould you like to listen?<br>mod<pg>Shamo<br>modThis juicy rumor comes from a mate in the<br>modsouth. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modThey said that some rogue Monkans are<br>modkidnapping minions! <br>modBe careful out there. <nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modTa-dah!<br>mod<br>mod<pg>Shamo<br>modI heard there’s a secret chest in the beach <br>modthat can only be revealed by, get this, <br>modWALKING!<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modSomeone out there must know more info<br>modabout this. <br>modBut for now...<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modTa-dah! <br>mod<br>mod<pg>Shamo<br>modSomeone is looking for rare peppers in Pica <br>modPica Island. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modI heard she’s willing to pay with an awesome <br>modtreasure to anyone who helps her complete<br>modthe collection.<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modTa-dah!<br>mod<br>mod<pg>Shamo<br>mod<br>modThat’s it for today, curious kid! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modTa-dah!<br>mod<br>mod",
            "!Shamo<br>modPsst! <br>modYou! <br>modYes, you!<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modI have some new rumors! <br>modWould you like to listen? <br>mod<pg>Shamo<br>modRumor has it that the Great Baron of Long<br>modWoods has a secret study somewhere in his <br>modManor! <nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modIt’s so well hidden that even he doesn’t <br>modknow it’s there!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modWell, it’s more like he forgot where it is, but <br>modstill.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modTa-dah!<br>mod<br>mod<pg>Shamo<br>mod<br>modThis is more like a tip, but listen well!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modI heard that if your clothes get wet you can’t<br>modglide because you get heavier! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modSnow can do that, I think?<br>modAnyway, be careful!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modTa-dah! <br>mod<br>mod<pg>Shamo<br>mod<br>modThis one comes from the web!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modIf you throw a pellet at the chubby ghosts <br>modwhen their mouths are open, they will fall <br>modasleep! <nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modTa-dah!<br>mod<br>mod<pg>Shamo<br>mod<br>modThat’s it for today, curious kid! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modTa-dah!<br>mod<br>mod",
            "!Shamo<br>modI’m not going to that siege, I have a very <br>modimportant duty! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modSpread vague rumors about stuff! <br>modI’m a professional for crying out loud! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>mod<br>modSo, you want to hear the latest rumors?<br>mod<pg>Shamo<br>modAs you can see the castle is basically <br>moddeserted, but I heard Mr. Stitches is in his <br>modroom waiting for someone! <nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modNo one knows why he’s doing it, but until <br>modhe’s done with his business this siege won’t <br>modstart! <nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modTa-dah!<br>mod<br>mod<pg>Shamo<br>modI heard there’s a secret way down a perilous<br>modpitfall that hauls some wonderful secret! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>mod<br>modThis is of course in Heroes Road. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modTa-dah! <br>mod<br>mod<pg>Shamo<br>modA weird looking moth was seen heading to <br>modWorld 1! <br>modCould that be another rogue minion?<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modTa-dah!<br>mod<br>mod<pg>Shamo<br>modThat’s it for today, kid!<br>modI hope my rumors proved useful for your <br>modtravels! <nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>mod<br>modI bid you farewell! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Shamo<br>modTa-daaah!<br>mod<br>mod",
