            "!Tela<br>modWhat is this! <br>modWe have visitors, dear sisters.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Ara<br>mod<br>modYour so right, hah.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Nia<br>mod<br>modIt’s “you’re”, Ara.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Ara<br>mod<br>modThis is a verbal conversation, Nia.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Tela<br>modSILENCE, YOU LOUDMOUTHS. <br>modWE HAVE GUESTS.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Tela<br>modI, Tela, welcome you to the great Baron <br>modvan Gregory’s room. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modYeah, yeah. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modListen, we just need to take a quick look <br>modinside the tower and see if the Baron is <br>modthere. We have something for him.<nl>!MOD!Ara<br>mod<br>modOh, oh, is it shiny?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Nia<br>modIs it that little masked kid right there?<br>modThey’re so delicious!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod!?!<br>mod<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Tela<br>mod<br>modThey certainly are! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modHey! <br>modStay away from the kid!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Bella<br>modOh, not these three. <br>modThey’re k-known bullies over here. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Bella<br>modThey’re probably just blocking the way to <br>modr-rob people.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Ara<br>mod<br>modWe usually do, yeah!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Tela<br>modBut we only take masked kids as payment,<br>modas of now…<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Tela<br>modNAHAHAHA!<br>mod<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modWhy don’t you give them a taste, kid?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod!!!<br>mod",
