            "!Takashi<br>modAlways be on the lookout <br>modfor potions. They heal<br>modyour wounds completly!<pg>Takashi<br>modYou can increase your <br>modcapacity for carrying potions <br>modin your inventory!<nl>!MOD!Takashi<br>modJust visit the Evil Store<br>modto the right from here.<br>modCan't miss it!<nl>!MOD!Takashi<br>modThose are pricey, so <br>modyou've been warned!<br>mod",
            "!Taeru<br>modI’ve seen how the Don looks at <br>modMr. Stitches when they talk. <br>modIt’s pretty obvious.<nl>!MOD!Taeru<br>modI can’t help but feel like Lord Stitches is <br>modtaking advantage of that…<br>mod",
            "!T. Bur<br>modWhen I found out the hero had died, I was<br>modgoing to start the cycle all over again, <br>modbut Mr. Stitches stopped me. <nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modHe planned some kind of experiment for <br>modyou... He wanted to see what course of <br>modaction you would take, I suppose.<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modStitches is… waiting for you in his room, <br>modactually. It is almost like he wants you to<br>modfight him.<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modThis is just a game to him.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modPerhaps not… he must have his reasons, <br>modeven if they make sense only to him.<br>mod",
            "!T. Bur<br>modThis is nothing personal, 745. <br>modI’m actually quite fond of you. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>mod<br>modYou remind me of him...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modBut like I said, I can’t let you hurt <br>modMr. Stitches. <br>mod<pg>T. Bur<br>mod<br>modThis conversation is over… Have at you! <br>mod<pg>T. Bur<br>mod<br>modEnough! I give up!<br>mod<pg>T. Bur<br>modI’ve been observing you, 745. <br>modEver since you dropped that chandelier <br>modon your fellow underlings, and the hero… <nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modI tasked my assistant Frankie to <br>modinvestigate your past.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modYou are a very lonely individual, 745.<br>modYou have always been a quiet one, so <br>modquiet that it bothers the ones around you. <nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modPerhaps because of fear, they treated <br>modyou like an outsider, an alien among<br>modthem.<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modYou resented your peers. <br>modI could almost feel an air of… satisfaction, <br>modwhen you disposed of your enemies.<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modBut, now? <br>modYou have changed considerably!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modYou have found friends, people who <br>modbelieve in you. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modYou no longer do it for payback, or the <br>modexcuse of riches. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modJust look at you!<br>modYou are standing here, trying to rescue <br>modyour friends. To set them free! <nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>mod<br>modYou’re now fighting to set them all free...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modAnd I’m just here, trying to defend...<br>moda madman. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>mod<br>mod...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modYou have reminded me why we did this <br>modin the first place...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>mod<br>modTo be free.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>mod<br>modYou’re a good listener, 745.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modI need to make this right, so… <br>modI have decided to help you. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modCall your friends, we need all the help we<br>modcan get.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod!<br>mod<pg>Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modKID!<br>mod<pg>Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modI can’t believe you fought alone. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modI’m sorry… I think I lost myself for a<br>modmoment there.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Cereza<br>modYour fight has reminded us why we want <br>modto defeat Stitches, green boots. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modIt seems I wasn’t the only one who lost <br>modhis way.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modI haven’t forgotten what you did, fish! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modI can’t come close to atone for my <br>modmistakes, but I can start by helping you. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modOn the condition that you don’t... <br>modkill Stitches. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modSomething is really wrong with him and I<br>modwant to help him. But his madness has to<br>modstop. I can treat him after you defeat him.<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modHow can we trust you!? <br>modAfter all the lies, after-<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod…Very well. <br>modIf you trust him I guess I trust him too,<br>modkid.<nl>!MOD!Cereza<br>modWhat’s the plan here? <br>modJust fighting Stitches!?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modNo. <br>modI said they had a chance, but it is still <br>modvery unlikely you will defeat him all alone. <nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>mod<br>modWe will need help from the bosses.  <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modTHEM!? <br>modWhat makes you think they’ll help!?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modThey don’t particularly love Stitches. <br>modHe… WE have done terrible things to them.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Cereza<br>modThey’re strong, I’ll give you that.<br>modHow do we do this?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modI’ll control the army of minions. <br>modThey’re supposed to attack the kingdom<br>modvery soon.<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modI will try to convince them and make time,<br>modwhile you look for the bosses.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modWe can go have a talk with Alexandria<br>modand Greg. <br>modBut El Salserissimo…<nl>!MOD!Cereza<br>modLeave the big lizard to me! <br>modYou go convince those two!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modAfter you get them, I will open the way to<br>modHeroes Road.  <br>modIt’s the only way to reach Stitches now.<nl>!MOD!T. Bur<br>modBehind me, you’ll find a secret elevator<br>modthat leads back to the castle. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modGot it. Let’s go!<br>mod<pg>T-Bur<br>mod<br>modno ai rial? ok :(<br>mod",
