            "!Mr. Stitches<br>modThis last stone belongs to the guardian of <br>modPica Pica Island, a ruthless salamander <br>modunder my command.<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modHe is known as…<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>mod...El Salserissimo.  <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modAlready at the last stone! <br>modYou’re a miracle worker. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modDon’t think I have forgotten about your <br>modreward… <br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod*Gulp*<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modA PROMOTION, OF COURSE! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modYou’ll be promoted for your efforts.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod!!!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modWe will talk about it in more detail the next<br>modtime we see each other! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modThe next time… Hehehe.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modEven I can’t predict what will happen...<br>modHow...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modAmusing!<br>mod",
            "!Mr. Stitches<br>modHehehe, you have arrived.<br>modWelcome!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modOf course we have!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modIt’s time to end this, Stitches! <br>modOnce and for all!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modOnce and for all… Heh…<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modI was afraid it would come to this.<br>modI even sent my special soldiers to stop you.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modLike that dirty trick was going to stop us!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modYou are truly heartless… <br>modI thought you would come to your senses. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modI thought I could save you from this never<br>modending fate.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modBut here you stand…<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modWhat the heck are you talking about!? <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modStop it with the evil monologue, and let's<br>modfight!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modHA!<br>modHA!<br>modHA!<pg>Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modUgh… heh…<br>mod<pg>Cereza<br>mod<br>modGuys, you did it!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modPrincess!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modNo please! <br>modNo more! <br>modI give up! <nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modMercy!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modGet up, you clown!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modYou’re so lying...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>mod…Heh.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modHehehehehe.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modHAHAHAHAHAHA<br>mod<br>mod<pg>Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modNow, you hide...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modAnd I seek...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Cereza<br>mod<br>modWhat is going on!?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Bella<br>modG-guys! <br>modThere is no blue fire here! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Bella<br>modI’m afraid we can’t help you...<br>modBe careful.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modPrincess!? <br>modWhere are you!? <br>modKid, we need to find her!<nl>!MOD!Bella<br>modI don’t think Stitches can see us in this <br>modd-darkness… but he can definitely hear us.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modKid! Don’t you dare jump now! <br>modYou’ll make less noise that way. <br>modDon’t let him see you!<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modFind Cereza!<br>mod<pg>Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modPrincess!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Cereza<br>modShh! <br>modI have a backup plan!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Cereza<br>mod<br>modW-What do we do!?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Cereza<br>modI’ve got these explosives I stole from the<br>modclone factory.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modThat sounds dangerous… I like it.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Cereza<br>modI’m going to set them up in every column  <br>modof this room. While I do that, I need you<br>modto activate every single bomb!  <nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod!?!<br>mod<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Cereza<br>modJust do it! <br>modAfter every bomb is active, we'll get out of<br>modhere.<nl>!MOD!Cereza<br>mod<br>modAnd be quiet!<br>mod<pg>Elizabeth IV<br>modThat’s it! <br>modWhat now!?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Cereza<br>modNow we escape! <br>modGREG!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<br>mod<br>modThat’s the signal!<br>mod<pg>Ghosty<br>modWe will get you guys to safety.<br>modThe Baron sent us!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Bella<br>mod<br>modThe G-great Baron!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Handy<br>mod!!!<br>mod<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modHow about we hug each other later, huh?<br>modBOMBS, remember!?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Ghosty<br>mod<br>modHang on!<br>mod<pg>Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modHello, masked child.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modThank you for doing what I requested.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modAll the stones have been returned to their <br>modowners, and your mission is finally over.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modYou even let my guards live, how merciful <br>modof you.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modI was hoping they could knock some sense<br>modinto you.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modI thought I could save you from this never <br>modending fate, but alas...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modStop playing dumb!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modYou knew we were coming...<br>modYou let us free since the beginning...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modFor what purpose!?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modAh, Elizabeth.<br>modYes, I knew everything from the start.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modI was so surprised when I heard the hero<br>modwas dead...<br>modIt has never happened before, you see.<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modWell, at least not like this...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modWhat do you mean? <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modWhen I was young, I worked under a <br>modpowerful Queen.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modShe was… ruthless, worked us until <br>modexhaustion. She saw us, her underlings, <br>modas lesser beings.<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modIn her eyes, we were just obstacles to be<br>modlaid before the heroes.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modI lost many friends... good friends.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modSo one day, I decided I had enough...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modAnd I killed her.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>mod!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modWhat I did not understand at the time, was<br>modthat she had a reason for her ruthlessness.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modShe needed to be strong, for she held a <br>modterrible weight upon her shoulders...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modIf she stopped fighting the heroes, the <br>modworld would... end.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modThe hero cycle...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod...Voices in my head, they spoke of my<br>moddreadful fate.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modI had to become the new villain of the <br>modstory, but that did not mean I had to be<br>modlike my Queen.<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modI wanted to keep the friends I had left out<br>modof harm’s way, but I also needed their <br>modstrength.<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modJust because they’re clones doesn’t mean <br>modyou could treat them like trash!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modAnd you treated them any better?<br>modYou always saw them as obstacles, too. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modSweet experience points, right?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>mod...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modAnd you! <br>modYou just blindly followed Elizabeth’s every<br>modcommand...<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modYou killed your way to me, without ever<br>modasking yourself why.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modShe did not even have to ask you nicely.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod...I didn’t leave the kid much choice... what<br>modI did wasn’t right. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modI know that now...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modBut even if we can never atone for what <br>modwe did, we still have to stop you! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modI just wanted to warn you...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>modIf you defeat me, you will have to take  <br>modmy place.  <br>modSomeone has to...<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod!?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modSo what, just because a voice in your head<br>modtold you the world was going to end, you<br>modjust followed blindly!?  <nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modDon’t you think that sounds a little bit <br>modinsane!? <br>modYou hypocrite!<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>mod...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modWe are going to beat you, Stitches, and we<br>modare going to prove that these cycles are <br>modjust in your head!<nl>!MOD!Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modI cannot take that risk.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modThen stop monologuing and let’s<br>modFIGHT!<br>mod<pg>Mr. Stitches<br>mod<br>modCOME AND GET ME, FOOLS!<br>mod<pg>Mr. Stitches<br>modI will not let you destroy the world, you<br>modFOOLS!<br>mod",
