            "!Josh the guard<br>modThis way leads to the main castle. I’m <br>modunder strict orders from Lord Stitches<br>modto not let anyone past this point. <pg>Josh the guard<br>modThe upper floors are also known as <br>modHeroes Road.        <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Josh the guard<br>modIt’s the path the heroes must take to face <br>modLord Stitches.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Josh the guard<br>modWe live separately from that castle, so you <br>modcan relax.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Josh the guard<br>mod<br>modNo hero is getting down here!<br>mod",
