            "!Jilani<br>modI am a collector of rare peppers that are <br>modfound deep in the jungle of this island.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Jilani<br>modI’m currently missing a few of them, but <br>modI’m afraid of going into the jungle myself.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Jilani<br>modThat place is scary and disorienting… I do <br>modNOT want to get lost in there, again...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Jilani<br>modSay, if you happen to find some of the <br>modpeppers I’m lacking, could you bring them<br>modto me?<nl>!MOD!Jilani<br>modI'm looking for a blue pepper, a red pepper,<br>modand a green pepper.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Jilani<br>mod<br>modI will trade them all for a special prize! <br>mod<pg>Jilani<br>modThank you! <br>modBut you haven’t found all my missing <br>modpeppers...<nl>!MOD!Jilani<br>modI'm looking for a blue pepper, a red pepper,<br>modand a green pepper.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Jilani<br>modIf you find all of them I’ll give you <br>modsomething great!<br>mod<pg>Jilani<br>modTHIS IS IT!!! <br>mod<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Jilani<br>modMy collection is finally complete! <br>modThank you so much! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Jilani<br>modPlease, take this as thanks for your hard<br>modwork.<br>mod<pg>Jilani<br>modMy collection is complete! <br>modAnd it's all thanks to you.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Jilani<br>mod<br>modCan't wait to show off.<br>mod",
