            "!Elizabeth IV<br>modYour place looks safe enough, I guess? <br>modAlright.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod*Ahem*<br>mod<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modGreetings, my name is Elizabeth IV, and I<br>modam a magical hilt. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modI have chosen you as my companion to free<br>modthis world of evil.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modDo you accept your destiny as the chosen <br>modhero of legend?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod!!!<br>mod<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod…That’s it? <br>modUmm… Good enough, I guess? <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modI did give you the short speech, the long<br>modone is at least 8000 words longer.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modSo, what’s your name? <br>modAre you a girl or-<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modRight. <br>modHow about this, I’ll just call you “kid”.<br>modCool?<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modVery well, kid. <br>modWe have no time to lose if we want to <br>moddefeat that Stitches guy. <nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modHe might look goofy but he IS the evil king,<br>modafter all.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod...?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modWhat? <br>modOf COURSE we have to fight him! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modDidn’t you see what he did to his own <br>modminion!? <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modHe’s obviously going to get rid of you once <br>modyou finish that “mission” of his.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modCalm down, we can do this. <br>modYou have ME, after all!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modOne thing you must know, though. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modWhen I change “bearers” I lose all of my<br>modpowers, so we need to train and get strong<br>modenough to defeat Mr. Stitches!<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modHere’s what I propose:<br>modWe play along with Stitches’ mission so he<br>moddoesn’t suspect a thing. <nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modWe’ll fight with all the bosses and we will <br>modbecome stronger... together.  <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modHelp me defeat him, kid!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modFine, and you can take all his coins after <br>modwe’re done with him.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod!!!<br>mod<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modAlright, alright. Now, there’s gotta be a way<br>modyou minions move between worlds, right? <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modI mean, you guys always get there first, <br>modsomehow.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modLet’s get going, kid. <br>modTo the forest!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modWait!<br>mod<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modOne last thing! If you wanna talk about the <br>modplace we are currently in, just press the<br>mod$$input012  <nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modTry not to bother me so often.<br>mod",
