            "!Elizabeth IV<br>modUp ahead, kid!<br>modOur first enemy. <br>modSweet experience points, baby!<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modSince you look like a wimp, I’m gonna have<br>modto teach you how to fight like a real hero!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modFor better or for worse, we are a team <br>modnow so you better pay attention.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modIf you're struggling with an enemy, you can<br>modtalk to me in battles with the $$input012  <br>modDon't forget it!  <nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modNow, approach that monster!<br>mod",
