            "!Elizabeth IV<br>modTime for more training, kid! <br>modThis just occurred to me, but…<br>mod<pg>Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modYou can totally talk to your enemies! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modYou’re all minions, after all, but you can<br>modonly talk before attacking your enemies. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modLearning new info is important, so make<br>moda habit of talking before attacking.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modNow, talk to that enemy by pressing <br>modthe $$input003  <br>mod<pg>Elizabeth IV<br>modThat’s your potions button, you can use <br>modit to replenish 50% of your HP.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modTo use it just press the $$input004  <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modSo uh...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modYour face is a mess, yo!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Testela<br>mod<br>modY-you said wha!? <br>mod<pg>Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modNow kid, use a potion!<br>mod<pg>Elizabeth IV<br>modIf you don't wanna end up broke, you<br>modbetter fight your battles like I told ya!<br>modBribing grants less experience, after all.<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modAfter you pay them enough coins, they will<br>modleave you alone and you won't be able to <br>modfight them again.<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modThat's it for now.<br>modOk, back to battle!<br>mod<pg>Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modUh, good to know I guess?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modNext up is your HP, up there. <br>modIf that number reaches zero, it’s game <br>modover, obviously.<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modSO, to avoid your early demise you can <br>moduse this!<br>mod<pg>Elizabeth IV<br>modThere you go! <br>modFeeling better?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modYou can use potions outside of battles, too!<br>modPress the $$input016 3 times; one to show<br>modthe hud, and two more to confirm!<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modNow, it's time for desperate measures.<br>modIf you feel like you need to flee a battle...<br>modWell...<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modYou could bribe your foes!<br>mod<pg>Elizabeth IV<br>modThe only way to stop your enemies from<br>modattacking you, is with money!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modYour coins appear in the down right corner <br>modof the screen there. <br>modMake sure you have enough!<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modTo pay coins to your enemies, just press<br>modthe $$input013  <br>modLet's try it!<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modPAY UP!<br>mod",
            "!Elizabeth IV<br>modThis thing is missing a fuse... great! <br>modJust, great. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modWhat now, genius!? <br>modWhere the heck are we going to find a fuse<br>modfor a-<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modWait... do you hear that?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modIt sounds like...<br>moda couple of idiots are having a <br>modconversation...<pg>Tim<br>modGolly, Mr. Timbolt! <br>modI can’t wait to meet mommy!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Timbolt<br>modYes, yes, quite so, dear Tim! <br>modBut I’m afraid the elevator is not functional <br>modat the moment.<nl>!MOD!Tim<br>modBut Mr. Timbolt! <br>modWhy don’t we just fly up there with our <br>modwings?<nl>!MOD!Timbolt<br>modNonsense, boy! <br>modWe must arrive to mother in… <br>modan elegant fashion!  <nl>!MOD!Tim<br>mod<br>modWhat’s a fashion, sir?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Timbolt<br>modAlas, the elevator is missing a fuse, dear <br>modTim. <br>modWhat to do...<nl>!MOD!Tim<br>modOh, maybe those grown-ups down there <br>modknow where to find the fews!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Timbolt<br>modBrilliant, Tim! <br>modWe shall ask them politely, like I taught you.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Tim<br>mod<br>modOkey-dokey!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Timbolt<br>mod<br>modExcuse me, lasses!<br>mod<pg>Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modThis can’t end well…<br>mod<pg>Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modAnd it didn’t.<br>mod<pg>Gang Boss<br>modOh, yeah. <br>modWe trashed that pretty butterfly real good,<br>modgurl!<nl>!MOD!Mothy Chief<br>modHe wanted a fuse for the elevator <br>modapparently, but the only place he’ll find one<br>modis at the bottom of this tree.  <nl>!MOD!Gang Boss<br>modYeah, there’s no way we are letting <br>modunderage kids go down there. That’s why<br>modI beat them up and set them straight!<nl>!MOD!Mothy Chief<br>modGood thing we locked the only way down<br>modthere with 2 locks, like the Queen ordered.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Gang Boss<br>modOh yeah, she’ll be pleased to know that <br>modher children are not going to dangerous<br>modplaces.<nl>!MOD!Mothy Chief<br>mod<br>modWe better take these keys to a safe place.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Gang Boss<br>modAgreed.<br>modYou take one and I’ll take the other.<br>mod<pg>Mothy Chief<br>modAll done here, back to work then. <br>modSee ya!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Gang Boss<br>modOh right, work. <br>modBetter go back with the gang.<br>mod<pg>Elizabeth IV<br>modWell, at least we know where to find a <br>modfuse now… <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modBut on top of that, now we need to find <br>modtwo keys…<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modGOSH THIS IS SO CONVOLUTED.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>mod*Sigh*<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modLead the way, kid.<br>mod<pg>Tester<br>mod<br>modare<br>mod<pg>Tester<br>mod<br>modyou<br>mod<pg>Tester<br>mod<br>modman?<br>mod",
            "!Elizabeth IV<br>modThis painting seems… different from the <br>modone in the other room.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modWhat could this mean?<br>mod",
            "!Elizabeth IV<br>modThese guys are rather tough, kid.<br>modI think it’s time for me to teach you our <br>modstrongest and final technique!<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modPay close attention, it’s a bit tricky to<br>modmaster.<br>mod<pg>Elizabeth IV<br>modIt’s called rush mode! And it can unleash<br>moda powerful chain of sword combos. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modTo activate rush mode, you need both your<br>modstamina meter and your rush meter to be<br>modcompletely full. <nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modWhat is the rush meter, I hear you ask? <br>mod<pg>Elizabeth IV<br>modIt’s this circular meter behind my pretty <br>modface in the battle menu. It charges up by <br>modgiving and receiving damage.<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modOnce both are full, activate rush mode <br>modby pressing $$input009 simultaneously.  <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modReady?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modActivate it!<br>mod<br>mod<pg>Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modRush mode is now active! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modNoticed how the music is quieter now, and <br>moda beat can be heard?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modThat’s because you must hit your foe to <br>modthe beat of the music to chain powerful <br>modcombos! <nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modNo need to worry about your stamina, <br>modsince it will slowly drain while this mode <br>modis active anyway. <nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modIf you fail to hit a beat you will lose your<br>modcombo, but you can keep trying while <br>modyour stamina lasts. <nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modIt’s a bit complicated, but let’s try it. <br>modUse your sword to hit with the beat. <br>modReady? <nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modGO!<br>mod<br>mod<pg>Elizabeth IV<br>modYou felt that? <br>modThis was just a demonstration.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modThe real deal is much harder, but you’ll <br>modmaster it with time. Noticed how your <br>modenemy is in a stunned state? <nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modEvery time you use rush mode, you don’t <br>modhave to worry about blocking or evading.<br>modJust hit those beats!<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modIf for whatever reason you want to cancel <br>modrush mode, simply press $$input009 again.  <br>mod<pg>Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modAnd that’s all I have to teach you, kid! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modRemember these lessons well. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modBack to battle!<br>mod",
            "!Elizabeth IV<br>modThere’s gotta be a way we can find out <br>modabout Greg’s lost memories, and my own <br>modpast…<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modBut how?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod…Never mind, kid. <br>modSaving the kingdom, no, the world, is more<br>modimportant right now!<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modWe can think about solving the past after <br>modwe save the future.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Handy<br>mod<br>mod*CLAPS*<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modWas that sarcastic?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>mod<br>mod...And how can you even clap?  <nl>!MOD!Bella<br>mod<br>modOh no, he was actually v-very moved!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>mod…Was that sarcastic?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modKid... you laughed.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modYou can actually laugh!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Bella<br>mod<br>modIt is a pretty l-laugh.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modAlright team, Pica Pica Island here we go!<br>mod",
            "!Elizabeth IV<br>modThere he goes! <br>modAfter him!<br>mod<pg>Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modWe are not going back that way.<br>mod<pg>Tester<br>modTest Line 1<br>modTest Line 2<br>modTest Line 3<nl>!MOD!Tester<br>modTest Line 1<br>modTest Line 2<br>modTest Line 3<nl>!MOD!Tester<br>modTest Line 1<br>modTest Line 2<br>modTest Line 3<nl>!MOD!Tester<br>modTest Line 1<br>modTest Line 2<br>modTest Line 3<nl>!MOD!Tester<br>modTest Line 1<br>modTest Line 2<br>modTest Line 3<pg>Tester<br>modTest Line 1<br>modTest Line 2<br>modTest Line 3<nl>!MOD!Tester<br>modTest Line 1<br>modTest Line 2<br>modTest Line 3<nl>!MOD!Tester<br>modTest Line 1<br>modTest Line 2<br>modTest Line 3<nl>!MOD!Tester<br>modTest Line 1<br>modTest Line 2<br>modTest Line 3<nl>!MOD!Tester<br>modTest Line 1<br>modTest Line 2<br>modTest Line 3<pg>Tester<br>modTest Line 1<br>modTest Line 2<br>modTest Line 3<nl>!MOD!Tester<br>modTest Line 1<br>modTest Line 2<br>modTest Line 3<nl>!MOD!Tester<br>modTest Line 1<br>modTest Line 2<br>modTest Line 3<nl>!MOD!Tester<br>modTest Line 1<br>modTest Line 2<br>modTest Line 3<nl>!MOD!Tester<br>modTest Line 1<br>modTest Line 2<br>modTest Line 3",
