            "!Elizabeth IV<br>modThat’s the Moth Queen’s big tree. <br>modIf we can reach the top, we can take her on.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modBut it looks like they locked the door with <br>moda special lock, so it probably needs a <br>modspecial-looking key. <nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modLet’s find it!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modOh, and by the way.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modIf you happen to get stuck, you can read<br>modthat journal of yours in the Items Menu.  <br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod!?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modNo, calm down...<br>modI didn't read it.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>mod<br>mod...That much.  ",
