            "!Elizabeth IV<br>modSo hey, you mentioned you were looking<br>modfor something here?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Tim<br>mod<br>modYes, our pretty hat!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Timbolt<br>modMy memory has been a little fuzzy as of <br>modlate. But Tim and I managed to escape <br>modthis wretched dungeon not so long ago. <nl>!MOD!Tim<br>mod<br>modBut we forgot our hat here!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Timbolt<br>modI cannot for the life of me remember why,<br>modbut it is a very special item for us, for<br>modsome reason.<nl>!MOD!Tim<br>modDon’t worry, T. <br>modWe’ll get it back.<br>mod",
            "!Elizabeth IV<br>modShow yourself, Greg! <br>modWe have come to- <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modHe’s not here, is he?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>mod*Sigh*<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modSay… <br>modwhat is that weird floating thing there…<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Bella<br>mod<br>modThat is one of the Baron’s r-relics. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Bella<br>modYou need 3 of those mementos if you<br>modwish to enter his secret c-chamber.  <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod…And Greg is in this secret chamber, isn’t <br>modhe?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Bella<br>mod<br>modMost probably, y-yes!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modThen WHY didn’t you tell US!?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Bella<br>modY-you never asked! <br>modAnd to be frank, you never told u-us <br>modwhat you wanted to do in the first place!<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modWell… true, but-<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<br>mod<br>modIf it isn't my favorite kiddo!<br>mod",
