            "!Elizabeth IV<br>modOh no! It’s a blizzard, kid! <br>modThese cold winds will definitely harm you!  <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modPlus, you won't be able to glide with your<br>modhoodie because of the snow.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modLook! It seems the left side is blocked... <br>modOr at least until the blizzard stops.<br>modLet's come back later.<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modBut nevermind that!<br>modWe need to find some shelter first.<br>modThe manor shouldn't be too far away!",
