            "!Elizabeth IV<br>modHellooooo?<br>modAnybody here? <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modShow your face, you coward! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modWhat the…!? <br>modYou’re not Stitches! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Grey Kid<br>modYeah, thanks for stating the obvious.<br>modThis is a trap, in case you hadn’t noticed.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modOkay. <br>modI thought the whole rival thing was<br>modcute before, but you’re a bit too late pal. <nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modWe’re hours away from facing Stitches, <br>modand if you don’t back off it will be game <br>modover for you too.<nl>!MOD!Grey Kid<br>modNo one will stop me from taking what<br>modis rightfully mine! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Grey Kid<br>modOnly I will have the satisfaction of <br>modbringing Stitches down, and saving the <br>modkingdom once and for all!<nl>!MOD!Grey Kid<br>mod<br>modBrace yourself, green boots.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modWoah! <br>modLook out, kid! <br>mod",
            "!Elizabeth IV<br>modHAH! WE GOTCHA!<br>mod<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Bella<br>modP-please don’t hurt us!<br>modWe are not looking for trouble.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modWe don’t wanna hurt you! <br>modWe actually need your help.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Bella<br>modD-did you hear that, Handy? <br>modThey just w-wanted our help, that’s it!<br>modNo need to run away, you silly goose. <nl>!MOD!Handy<br>mod<br>mod...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modOh, you have a silent partner too!? <br>modWhat a coincidence!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Bella<br>modYes! His name is Handy and I am B-Bella.<br>modNice to meet you.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Bella<br>modI’m h-helping Handy find his body so he <br>modcan become w-whole again!<br>modThis place can be very… dark at times.<nl>!MOD!Handy<br>mod!!!<br>mod???<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Bella<br>modHe is a-asking if you have seen a body <br>modmissing a hand around here?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Bella<br>modI skipped certain words from his question,<br>modjust so you know. <br>modHe can be quite r-rude.<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modEhh… Not really, no… <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Handy<br>mod<br>mod*SNAP*<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modBut! We move around a lot.<br>modI’m sure that if you follow us in our travels,<br>modwe’ll be able to find your body eventually. <nl>!MOD!Bella<br>mod<br>modOH, I-I-I love traveling! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Bella<br>mod<br>modThis place can get really boring at times. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modIt’s settled, then! <br>modBut I do have a question before we get<br>modgoing.<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modWe need to reach the second floor, do you<br>modknow how to bring back the stairs?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Bella<br>mod<br>modHmm, we don’t really use the staircase.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Bella<br>modBut if I remember correctly, there should<br>modbe a way to a-activate it from the storage<br>modroom.<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modGot it. <br>modLet’s go, kid!<br>mod",
