            "!Day: OX - Month: VX<br>mod<br>modDay: OX - Month: VX<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Day: OX - Month: VX<br>modThree years have passed since I saved <br>modthis world. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Day: OX - Month: VX<br>modThe kingdom is at peace, the people of<br>modthe kingdom love me, I am young and <br>modhealthy… <nl>!MOD!Day: OX - Month: VX<br>modEver since I parted ways with her, ever<br>modsince that battle… <br>modI have felt unease… <nl>!MOD!Day: OX - Month: VX<br>modI will just try to forget about it, yes! <br>modJust try to forget.<br>mod...<nl>!MOD!Day: OI - Month: VX<br>mod<br>modDay: OI - Month: VX<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Day: OI - Month: VX<br>modI had that same terrible feeling last<br>modnight. My thoughts prevented my sleep. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Day: OI - Month: VX<br>modI decided to investigate that castle so <br>modthis anxiousness could go away… but <br>modthat was a mistake. <nl>!MOD!Day: OI - Month: VX<br>modMy eyes must have been deceiving me… <br>modI do not believe it.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Day: OI - Month: VX<br>modHow could he still be alive!? <br>modI defeated him, I am sure of it! Did he<br>modfake it? Was our battle just a farce? <nl>!MOD!Day: OI - Month: VX<br>mod<br>modIS HE MOCKING ME!?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Day: OI - Month: VX<br>modI cannot let the Kingdom know that he <br>modlives. They would hate me for it.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Day: OI - Month: VX<br>modTomorrow… <br>modI will kill that demon once and for all!<br>mod",
