br>modAww!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modHAHA!<br>modLet's go, kid.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod...<br>mod",
            "!Cheffa<br>modHey, you! <br>modWhere do you think you're going?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modOh! Um... We're here because... <br>modMr. Stitches sent us, yeah!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modTo deliver a... a very important message! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modTo El Salserissimo! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modUgh.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Cheffa<br>modLord Stitches, you say? <br>modDon Salserissimo will be very pleased to<br>modreceive this message!<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modCool!<br>modNow let us through.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Cheffa<br>mod<br>modGood luck!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Cheffa<br>mod<br>mod<br>modSucker...",
