            "!Queen Rena",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modWRONGO!  <br>modBoth T. Bur and Mr. Stitches worked under <br>moda greater evil, many years ago!<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modShe was a despicable Queen that ruled <br>modwith an iron fist!<br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modWRONGO!  <br>modAre you even trying at this point?<br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modWRONGO-BONGO!  <br>mod<br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modWRONG!!  <br>modARE YOU EVEN TRYING ANYMORE?<br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modWRONG!  <br>modWhat a way to go, folks! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modBetrayed by food! <br>modYou can’t trust anything anymore. <br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modWRONG!  <br>modShe was as healthy as one can be! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modShe ate her veggies and exercised <br>modregularly. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modSpeaking of health, that diet of potions <br>modand coffee can’t be good, kiddo. <br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modWRONG!  <br>modDid you even understand the question, <br>modkiddo?",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modWRONG!  <br>mod<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modMoney is one thing, but complete world <br>moddomination? <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modThat’s a thing only a truly evil being <br>modwould want!<br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modWRONG!  <br>mod<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modI made up that name just now. <br>modHow could you fall for that, kiddo?<br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modWRONG!  <br>mod<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modDon Salserissimo is a little too big to fit<br>modthese chambers!<br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modWRONG!  <br>mod<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modContrary to popular belief, the legendary <br>modhilt is dormant until it is paired with <br>moda hero. <nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modThe hilt has no bearing in this matter<br>modwhatsoever! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modWell this one is technically correct, since<br>modI DID choose this Masked Kid as the <br>modnew hero.<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>mod<br>modBut I don’t want to be called a traitor so<br>modI better keep my mouth shut...",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modWRONG!  <br>mod…Although, she has killed his reanimated <br>modcorpse many times in the past…<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>mod<br>modMOVING ON!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modI mean, of course I have… and he always <br>modcomes back. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modAre you not familiar with how zombies <br>modwork!?<br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modWelcome folks, to the amazing, the highly <br>modrated: PUZZLEMAN SHOW!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modIn tonight’s show we’ll tackle the SECOND <br>modquiz for our heroes! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modWhat mysteries lie ahead? <br>modLet’s find out!<br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modThis host regrets to inform you that this<br>modis indeed CORRECT!  <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modThe Queen lost her King thanks not to a <br>modclever move in chess, but to a rare <br>moddisease.<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modIt has kept the Moth King in a comatose <br>modstate for many, many years now. <br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modThe time has finally come! <br>modThe FINAL QUIZ for our contestants! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modWe have seen them grow, we have seen<br>modthem fail.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>mod<br>modBut tonight?<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>mod<br>modWE WILL SEE THEM WIN!<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Elizabeth IV<br>modLet’s get this over with, we have an Evil <br>modKing to defeat.<br>mod<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod...<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modBut before you do, let’s get this show on <br>modthe road, kiddo!<br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modThat would be the obvious answer… <br>modBut you are WRONG!!!  <br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modThat is CORRECT!  <br>modThe Baron loves only himself! <br>modMore accurately his young, beautiful self. <nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modThat’s right folks! Once he lost his youth <br>modhe experienced an extreme depression<br>modand died of sadness! <nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modThe only thing he remembers is his face, <br>modthanks to his numerous paintings <br>modadorning the manor! <nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modHe hides himself from the public in a secret <br>modchamber, just like a teenager. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modThree relics are needed to access said <br>modroom!<br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modTHANK YOU SO MUCH FOR PLAYING! <br>modIt has been a great season, folks! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modTwists and turns! Fights and adventures! <br>modBut I’m afraid all good things must come<br>modto an end! <nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modSo, this humble show host would like to <br>modwish you a good night, and may we see <br>modeach other next time in!<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modTHE<br>modPUZZLEMAN<br>modSHOW!",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modTHANK YOU FOR PLAYING! <br>modThat’s a wrap, folks! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modMay you all have a lovely evening and <br>modsee you next time in: <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modTHE<br>modPUZZLEMAN<br>modSHOW!",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modStay seated everyone, here comes the last<br>modand FINAL question! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modQUESTION #5<br>mod<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modHow did Mr. Stitches gain the trust and<br>modlove of the Moth Queen and her subjects?<br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modSo sorry, kiddo! You will leave empty<br>modhanded this time!<br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modSO ROMANTIC! <br>modAND SO WRONG!  <br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modResignation is not permitted for a villain, <br>modI’m afraid.<br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modNot everyone is as cheap as you, kiddo. <br>modWRONG!  <br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modNOT CORRECT!  <br>mod<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modHe was a hero alright, but not a chosen <br>modhero of legend or anything. <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modHe would remember things like fighting <br>modMr. Stitches or the legendary weapon <br>modotherwise! ",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modLaughable answer! <br>modAnd by that I mean WRONG answer! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modThe Moth Queen has literally hundreds of<br>modchildren! She may have already lost a few<br>modand didn’t even notice. <nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>mod<br>modCold as ice, folks!<br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modIS IT JUST ME? <br>modOR IS IT GETTING HOTTER IN HERE! <br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modQUESTION #2<br>mod<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modWhat substance is about to erupt from the <br>modvolcano?<br>mod",
            "!Puzzleman<br>modINCORRECT!  <br>mod<br>mod<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modHave you seen that guy!? <br>modHow could such an evil being have <br>modfriends!?<nl>!MOD!Puzzleman<br>modOf course he did it because he is truly <br>modmacabre!<br>modThe most evil being around!<nl>!MOD!<hero><br>mod<br>mod...<br>mod",
